  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A 3rd-person shooter in a sci-fi setting where you play as Kwabe, a space researcher partnered with Simon, a highly intelligent scientist cat. Together, you run a space research business, traveling to distant planets to complete contracts. But research isn’t your only challenge—Simon is always hungry and needs to be fed with anything you can find on these planets, including hostile creatures.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore 4 unique biomes, complete your contractrs, and don't forget to feed the cat!</p>",
